Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.53,0:00:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.49,0:02:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.54,0:02:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久很久以前，在遥远的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住了一对国王和王后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.41,0:02:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们一直盼望能有一个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.48,0:02:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女儿的诞生\N使他们多年的愿望实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们为公主取名奥萝拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.05,0:02:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奥萝拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奥萝拉就是黎明的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为小公主给他们的生活\N带来了阳光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于此同时\N全国沉浸在欢乐的节日中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人民不分高低贵贱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纷纷表达对小公主的敬意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.98,0:02:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纷纷表达对小公主的敬意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.91,0:02:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的故事\N就从这个欢乐的日子开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那欢乐时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.52,0:02:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那欢乐时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那欢乐时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.62,0:03:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们欢呼，庆贺公主诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.46,0:03:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,献上珍贵礼物和祝福\N以表达对她的忠诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.23,0:03:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向奥萝拉公主致敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全体臣民都敬爱她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.61,0:03:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国王万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.98,0:03:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王后万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.38,0:03:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝公主健康，祝公主健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万岁!公主奥萝拉
