Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.26,0:03:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.70,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝公主健康，祝公主健康
