Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.72,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主奥萝拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这个举国欢腾的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.86,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,整个王国庆祝这迟来的诞辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.13,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,史帝芬国王和王后\N正在欢迎一位他们世交的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈伯国王陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.38,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和菲利王子殿下驾到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两位君主都期待着有朝一日\N两个王国合并
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.29,0:04:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以他们今天将宣布\N哈伯国王的儿子菲利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和史帝芬国王的女儿订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.73,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小王子给小公主带来了礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他还不知道这就是他未来的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们尊敬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神圣的三位仙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花拉仙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翡翠仙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和蓝天仙子驾到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.88,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇，啊，可爱的小宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.16,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们每人送给孩子一个祝福\N不多不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一人一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小公主，我赐你稀世的美貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.11,0:06:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天赐稀世美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黄金秀发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阳光染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.29,0:06:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朱唇艳过红玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.56,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,青春欢乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.13,0:06:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永相随
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.14,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，小公主，我赐你美妙的歌喉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.56,0:06:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美妙歌喉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.66,0:07:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同渡过美好一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.00,0:07:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜莺唤来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多情歌手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.48,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小夜曲倾诉出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.21,0:07:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真挚爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宝贝小公主，我赐给你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，是黑巫婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她到这儿来干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.12,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，史帝芬国王\N真是个盛大的场面啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皇亲、国戚、贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.66,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，哈哈哈，真奇怪\N连平民也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没有收到请柬，这太让我难过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没人想邀请你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.41,0:08:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，亲爱的，这可太糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我本来希望这只是一时的疏忽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然如此，我只好走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，我们没有冒犯你吧，阁下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，没有，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了表示我没有恶意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.73,0:08:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要送给这个孩子一个祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们都给我听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.68,0:08:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主会长得楚楚动人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.25,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高雅美丽，人见人爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.92,0:09:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在她十六岁生日那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的手指将被纺车上的针刺破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她将立即死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，不!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.27,0:09:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈…哈…哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓住这个坏蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,退回去!笨蛋!\N哈…哈…哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陛下，请不要绝望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝天仙子还有一个祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那她可以破除这个可怕的咒语吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.76,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，我不行\N黑巫婆的法力太强大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是…\N-尽你的所能，亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对，快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.74,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对，快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亲爱的小公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万一你真的不幸被刺破了手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.88,0:10:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我送给你的祝福可以给你一线希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.48,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等待你的将不是死亡，而是沉睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要耐心等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.69,0:10:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个真心爱你的人给你的一个吻\N可以使你醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真诚的爱可以战胜一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.80,0:10:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真爱战胜一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.95,0:10:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,史帝芬国王\N仍然担心女儿的生命安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.08,0:10:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因而下令将全国的纺车烧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人民一律照办不误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.34,0:11:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑巫婆真是太可恨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，还是来喝杯茶吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总会想出办法来对付她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.59,0:11:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那，着急也阻止不了黑巫婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许我们可以跟她讲讲道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.73,0:11:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-讲道理？和黑巫婆吗？\N-她不可能一无是处呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她当然一无是处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.87,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真想把她变成一只丑陋的肥蛤蟆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亲爱的，你可不应该说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也办不到\N我们的法力做不了那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的法力只能做好事\N带给人们幸福欢乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是说说气话嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯定会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了，有办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么办法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心隔墙有耳啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要把她变成一朵花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-黑巫婆吗？\N-噢，不，不，不，我是说公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，那肯定是一朵可爱的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白吗？花不会被刺破手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花没有手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她就绝对安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.97,0:12:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑巫婆就会下一场大雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.20,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对呀，噢，不行\N黑巫婆总是把最美的花毁掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.91,0:12:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对\N而且她也能猜到咱们会那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.95,0:12:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么事她猜不到呢？\N她料事如神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.35,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，不，她不是，她不是无所不知\N她不懂得爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不懂得善更不懂得助人为乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.73,0:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想其实她自己也并不快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了，当然啦，她不懂的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯定也就永远猜不到，呵，呵，呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.91,0:13:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来，来，来，咱们得仔细安排一番\N让我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.24,0:13:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,林中小木屋，对，对\N当然国王和王后不会同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们必须告诉他们这是唯一的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.75,0:13:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么办法呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将由三个农妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.59,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在森林的深处，把孩子抚养成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，她们真是好心人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.23,0:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-她们是谁？\N-转过身去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.20,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，什么？是我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你是说咱们？\N-没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-照顾一个婴儿…\N-有问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，我喜欢这主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是个好主意，可是我们得喂她吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还要给她洗澡，穿衣，哄她入睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔，我喜欢干这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.95,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你真的认为咱们行吗？\N-凡人能做到咱们当然也能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.09,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-何况我们还有魔法\N-对啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.56,0:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不，不，不要用魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我们得把魔杖收起来\N-噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-背上的翅膀也不能用\N-你是说咱们要过凡人的日子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过十六年？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.31,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是如果不用魔杖\N咱们什么事也不会做呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是黑巫婆绝对猜不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-那么谁来洗衣做饭呢？\N-咱们一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.89,0:14:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我来照顾婴儿\N-把它给我，亲爱的，一起来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.43,0:14:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们现在就去见陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-花拉？\N-花拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国王和王后怀着沉重的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.78,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看着他们唯一心爱的女儿\N消失在夜幕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看着他们唯一心爱的女儿\N消失在夜幕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国王和他的人民\N在痛苦孤独中度过了十六年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随着公主十六岁生日的来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢乐又回到了这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是人人都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.18,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔鬼黑巫婆此时正在\N为她的预言没有实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而大发雷霆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而大发雷霆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.54,0:16:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经十六年了\N连她的影子都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.41,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不可能消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能肯定每个地方你都找过了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.81,0:16:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，每个地方都找遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，城市，森林，深山呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找遍了所有的大山和森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.53,0:16:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搜查了每一栋房子和每一个摇篮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摇篮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.90,0:16:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，每一个摇篮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.27,0:16:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摇篮？噢，你听见没有我的宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.24,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么多年来他们一直在找一个婴儿\N啊，哈哈哈，啊，哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.46,0:17:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白痴，废物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.35,0:17:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，废物，他们真是无可救藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.69,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，我的宝贝，我只能指望你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去飞得高高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去找一个十六岁的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.20,0:17:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她有着阳光般的金发玫瑰般的红唇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.17,0:17:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧，可别让我失望啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.35,0:17:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十六年来，没有人知道公主的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有在深山树林中的小木屋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.99,0:18:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三位好心的仙女\N小心翼翼地实行着她们的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她们把公主当作自己的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给她取名蔷薇玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是小公主十六岁生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.67,0:18:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仙女们打算举办一个生日晚会\N给她一个意外的惊喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看这个怎么样\N这个是我挑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.85,0:18:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-她穿这个一定很漂亮\N-我认为还需要改一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.89,0:18:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-嗯，哼，加一个蝴蝶结\N-肩部也要改一改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-要做成蓝色的\N-不，粉红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是…\N-当然还要加上一些裙褶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我们怎样才能\N让她离开一会儿呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来想个好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，你们三个人在这儿干什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-干什么？\N-干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.44,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-干什么？是…是…是…是这样\N-我们…我们…我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.48,0:18:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我们想让你去采草莓\N-对了，就是草莓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.11,0:18:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-草莓？\N-好多好多草莓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是我昨天才采过的呀!\N-啊，还…还…还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.09,0:19:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我们需要很多很多\N-是啊，哈…哈…哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不用急着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-别走得太远了\N-别和陌生人讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-再见，亲爱的\N-再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-再见\N-再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.84,0:19:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-不知道她会不会起疑心呢？\N-当然不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-快来吧，呵…呵…呵\N-她一定会大吃一惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真正的生日晚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要真正的生日蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对，还要一件真正的公主长裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.78,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我去取魔杖\N-好啊，啊，魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-啊，不…\N-不能用魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是十六年马上就要过完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们也不能轻易冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我从来没有做过蛋糕啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，别担心，亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.77,0:19:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我来做蛋糕好了\N-你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她一直想试一试\N这可是她最后的机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十五层的蛋糕\N用粉红和蓝色写成勿忘我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我来做衣服好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可你不会做衣服\N-她也根本不会作饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呵，呵，呵，这很简单\N照着书上做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上来，亲爱的，你可以当个衣架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.59,0:20:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是认为咱们应该用魔法\N呵，呵，呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.10,0:20:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面粉三杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.31,0:20:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杯子，杯子，杯子，啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.81,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一，二，三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.25,0:20:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-这是干什么呀？\N-是这样，我要在底下做个洞啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有洞，脚就没有地方站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.99,0:20:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-怎么是粉红色？\N-造型很美，对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.63,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是我想做成蓝色的\N-不是，亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.13,0:20:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-原来说好做粉红色的呀!\N-那是你说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.03,0:21:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，哼，噢，花拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.31,0:21:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你干什么呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个鸡蛋均匀地和在面粉里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和起来？啊，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喘不过气来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快让我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.43,0:21:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-难看极了\N-那是因为穿在你身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.84,0:21:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放一匙发粉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-一匙？\N-就是一汤勺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，就是一汤勺我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，这孩子长得好快呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们把她抱到这儿来\N就好像是昨天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那时她只是个小婴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.96,0:22:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你怎么了？蓝天\N-亲爱的，你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过了今天，她就是公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再也不是我们的蔷薇玫瑰了\N噢，花拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.34,0:22:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，是啊，是啊，我们都知道\N总会有这么一天的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这一天为什么来得那么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.38,0:22:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟她和我们在一起整整十六年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.25,0:22:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十六年的美好时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.36,0:22:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，多傻啊，快点吧\N不然来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.90,0:22:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点，蔷薇玫瑰很快就要回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.04,0:24:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听见了吗？大力士，多美啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.45,0:24:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁在唱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.72,0:24:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走，我们去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.55,0:24:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，好了，给你一桶燕麦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.43,0:24:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,外加胡萝卜，怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.03,0:24:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.30,0:24:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.56,0:25:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇，哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.38,0:25:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胡萝卜不给了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.39,0:25:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想知道想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.10,0:25:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.83,0:25:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小鸟总有知音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.90,0:26:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可献上甜蜜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.38,0:26:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢乐和爱情的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.02,0:26:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想知道想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.36,0:26:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我用心歌唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.93,0:26:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那歌声的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.97,0:26:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可否把他寻到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.81,0:26:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也带给我爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.44,0:26:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乐章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.42,0:26:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，天哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.86,0:26:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么她们总把我当成小孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.43,0:26:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么她们总把我当成小孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.30,0:27:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然是花拉，翡翠和蓝天阿姨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.10,0:27:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她们从来不让我见任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.51,0:27:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.75,0:27:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我骗了她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.91,0:27:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经见过一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.92,0:27:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，是一个王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.86,0:27:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他长得高大英俊而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.97,0:27:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且非常浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.84,0:27:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们在一起散步，我们在一起聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.61,0:27:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我们告别的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.91,0:27:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他拥抱了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.72,0:27:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后我就醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.36,0:28:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，那只是个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.43,0:28:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是人们常说如果\N你作两次相同的梦，梦就会成真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.07,0:28:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我梦见他好多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.78,0:28:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.05,0:28:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那声音给了我一种非常奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.08,0:29:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太美了，这不可能是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.52,0:29:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许是森林中的仙女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.42,0:29:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.73,0:29:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘿，站住，快停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.76,0:29:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天啊，这就是我梦见过的王子啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.37,0:29:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.57,0:30:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道我不该和陌生人说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.74,0:30:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我们曾经见过面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.85,0:30:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.78,0:30:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾与你在我梦中游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.12,0:30:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.96,0:30:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那熟悉的眼神看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.10,0:30:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.40,0:30:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现实不都像梦境般美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.21,0:30:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信你我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.27,0:30:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将一见钟情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.48,0:30:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就如梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.98,0:30:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情境一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.02,0:30:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无限美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.36,0:30:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信你我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.57,0:30:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将一见钟情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:58.44,0:31:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就如梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.51,0:31:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情境一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.14,0:31:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无限美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:09.48,0:31:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，哦…\N-真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.72,0:31:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吓着你了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.49,0:31:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，不，不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.26,0:31:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-只因你是个…是…\N-是个陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.29,0:31:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-对呀\N-难道你不记得了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.29,0:31:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们曾经见过面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.00,0:31:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我们见过面？\N-当然了，你自己说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.73,0:31:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在梦里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.67,0:31:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.07,0:31:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾与你在我梦中游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:40.01,0:31:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.88,0:31:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那熟悉的眼神看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.02,0:31:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.42,0:31:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.03,0:32:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现实不都像梦境般美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.50,0:32:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信你我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.17,0:32:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将一见钟情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.70,0:32:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就如梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.07,0:32:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情境一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.95,0:32:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.81,0:32:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.83,0:32:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是谁？你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.90,0:32:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.23,0:32:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，我叫…我…我叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.67,0:32:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，不，我不能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:43.64,0:32:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-再见了\N-什么时候能再见到你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.94,0:32:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，不能，永远不能\N-永远不能？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.45,0:32:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许，也许有一天能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.88,0:32:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哪一天？明天行吗？\N-哦，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.72,0:32:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，今晚吧\N-在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.22,0:32:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在小木屋峡谷那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.00,0:33:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.34,0:33:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，你们看怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.64,0:33:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，真是个很…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.21,0:33:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-很不一样的蛋糕，对不对？\N-是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.85,0:33:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，烤过之后就会硬点，对吗？\N-对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.99,0:33:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，烤过之后就会硬点，对吗？\N-对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.89,0:33:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看，衣服做得怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.79,0:33:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，它看上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.32,0:33:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，它看上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.79,0:33:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像和书上的样子不太一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.23,0:33:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，我改了一下\N也许再加上一些裙褶就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.17,0:33:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你说对不对呀？\N-啊，也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.50,0:33:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝天，你说呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.14,0:33:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，你们两个人胡闹够了没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.38,0:33:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此为止吧，你们也不想想\N搞了这么一团糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.02,0:34:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔷薇玫瑰她能高兴吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:00.35,0:34:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不管，我要去拿魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.96,0:34:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道吗？我想她是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.99,0:34:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔杖在这儿还和新的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.03,0:34:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小，小，小心一点儿，蓝天\N快把门锁上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.57,0:34:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翡翠，你去把窗户都关上\N一点儿缝隙都不要漏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.51,0:34:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千万别出事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.21,0:34:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在你把蛋糕做出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.95,0:34:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-那我…\N-去把屋子打扫干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.12,0:34:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我嘛，来做衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.62,0:34:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.46,0:34:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快来吧，水桶拖把快动手吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.16,0:34:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花拉说把屋子打扫干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.54,0:34:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.74,0:34:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为美丽的公主做一件\N无与伦比的衣服吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.18,0:35:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鸡蛋，面粉，牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.41,0:35:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照书上说的去做，我来把蜡烛插上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.04,0:36:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，不，不要粉红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.51,0:36:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.34,0:36:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，怎么搞的，粉红色？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:13.88,0:36:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.48,0:36:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.52,0:36:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,粉红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.86,0:36:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,粉红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.19,0:36:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.01,0:37:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，看你干的好事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.92,0:37:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘘，嘘，嘘，嘘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.92,0:37:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰她回来了\N-我看你闹够了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.89,0:37:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-粉红色\N-快藏起来，快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.07,0:37:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.57,0:37:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花拉阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.50,0:37:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的天啊，是谁让拖把在那儿飞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:46.08,0:37:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.01,0:37:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花拉阿姨，翡翠阿姨，蓝天阿姨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.02,0:37:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦，人都到哪儿去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.29,0:38:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-啊…\N-我们在这儿呢，亲爱的宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.29,0:38:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-祝你生日快乐!\N-你们真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.80,0:38:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我一生中最快乐的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.77,0:38:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都是如此美妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.20,0:38:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你们很快就要见到他了\N-啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.11,0:38:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰\N-你见到了陌生人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.28,0:38:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他不是陌生人，我们已经见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.75,0:38:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.25,0:38:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-在哪里？\N-在我的梦里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.48,0:38:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.12,0:38:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾与你在我梦中游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.46,0:38:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-啦哩啦啦\N-她坠入情网了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.79,0:38:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，不\N-这太糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.10,0:38:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？我现在已经十六岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:44.40,0:38:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是因为这，亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.17,0:38:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-因为你已经订过婚了\N-订过婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.37,0:38:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在你出生那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.84,0:38:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和菲利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.11,0:38:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是不可能的\N我怎么能嫁给王子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.85,0:38:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-除非我是…\N-一位公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.25,0:39:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你是公主，亲爱的\N-你是奥萝拉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.02,0:39:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚我们就将把你送还给你的父亲\N史帝芬国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.69,0:39:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，我不能走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.26,0:39:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他今晚要到这儿来\N我答应过要见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.53,0:39:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很抱歉，孩子\N今后你绝不能再见那个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.77,0:39:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不，我不相信这是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.51,0:39:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:29.85,0:39:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还以为她会很快乐呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.90,0:39:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉，还是看不到人影，哈伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.13,0:39:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然啦，太阳还没下山嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.44,0:40:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.68,0:40:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，来吧，来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.12,0:40:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是让我们干一杯吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.55,0:40:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起，哈伯，十六年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.52,0:40:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我提心吊胆整整十六年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.69,0:40:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过去了，一切都过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.03,0:40:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚让我们为未来干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:28.57,0:40:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这酒我整整存了十六年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.15,0:40:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来，为未来干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.31,0:40:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说得对，为未来干杯，哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:44.29,0:40:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来，干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.39,0:40:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干，为今夜干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.19,0:40:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我们前程似锦\N-前途真光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.03,0:40:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子结连理\N国土将一体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.97,0:41:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干杯，干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.21,0:41:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，真是好酒啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.48,0:41:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-现在，为新房干杯\N-新房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.02,0:41:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子们需要自己的家嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.12,0:41:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈，养育他们下一代的地方\N哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.56,0:41:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈伯，我想到了那个时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:25.40,0:41:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然了，为新房干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:29.30,0:41:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干，为新房干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.84,0:41:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比罗马宫殿还要富丽雄伟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.47,0:41:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为你斟满酒杯\N让忧伤一去不回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.58,0:41:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干杯，干杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.92,0:41:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.33,0:42:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.80,0:42:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实也没什么特别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.77,0:42:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四十间卧室和餐厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.00,0:42:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是度蜜月的小别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.04,0:42:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是说你已经在盖了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.01,0:42:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,盖好了，完工了\N明天就可以搬进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.11,0:42:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天？可是哈伯\N他们还没有结婚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.88,0:42:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就有劳你了，婚礼今晚举行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.08,0:42:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等，哈伯\N我还没见到我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.45,0:42:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你却打算把她从我身边带走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.09,0:42:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你喜欢我的菲利，对不对？\N-对，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.36,0:42:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你想不想见到我们的孙子？\N-当然想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.66,0:42:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还有什么可说的，不能再耽误了\N哈…哈…哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.93,0:42:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-为婚礼干杯\N-别不讲理好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.40,0:42:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的奥萝拉对这件事情\N还一无所知啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.14,0:42:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.28,0:42:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦？我是说\N也许会把她吓着的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.95,0:42:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？难道我的菲利可怕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.75,0:42:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的菲利有什么不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.45,0:43:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的，我的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.12,0:43:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的女儿为什么不爱我的儿子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.69,0:43:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.89,0:43:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许我儿子还不喜欢你的女儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.47,0:43:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听我说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:10.90,0:43:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许我的孙子还不喜欢\N你这个爷爷呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.34,0:43:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么这么不讲道理啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.51,0:43:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这个可恶的，讨厌的臭老头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.48,0:43:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不讲理，可恶，拿起你的剑，先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.85,0:43:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我警告你，哈柏\N这可意味着战争哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.35,0:43:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前进，为荣誉为国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.55,0:43:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为…呵，呵，哈…哈…哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.60,0:43:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-这到底是为了什么呢？\N-没事，哈伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.10,0:43:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-对不起，真的没事，哈伯\N-两个孩子肯定会彼此相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.47,0:43:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫无疑问，明天我就下令\N让皇家木匠开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:53.01,0:43:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为我们的孙子做摇篮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:55.71,0:43:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了，一定要大号的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:58.62,0:44:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然了，为木匠干杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:13.70,0:44:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利王子殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.10,0:44:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驾到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.24,0:44:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.88,0:44:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，菲利，菲利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:30.95,0:44:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利，菲利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:39.26,0:44:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点，儿子，快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:41.42,0:44:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去换换你的衣服\N总不能这个样子去见你的新娘吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.03,0:44:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我已经见过她了，爸爸!\N-见过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.80,0:44:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哦，在哪里？\N-在我的梦里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.47,0:44:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，菲利，快停下来，快停下来\N快点放我下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:57.74,0:45:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，你作了一个可笑的梦是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.98,0:45:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是作梦，爸爸，我真的见到她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:03.68,0:45:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,见到奥萝拉了？\N快把这个好消息告诉史帝芬，这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.15,0:45:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我没有说她是奥萝拉啊!\N-你当然说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.25,0:45:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你刚刚说过…\N-我遇见了一位姑娘，我要娶她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:14.59,0:45:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道她是谁\N可能是个农家姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:17.49,0:45:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,农农家姑娘？你要娶一个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:21.30,0:45:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈，菲利，你在开玩笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:27.40,0:45:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他在开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.34,0:45:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，你不能这样对待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.78,0:45:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为无名女子放弃王位\N放弃你的王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.88,0:45:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，我不准你这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.55,0:45:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是王子，你只能娶公主为妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.19,0:45:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父王，你可真是个老顽固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:49.86,0:45:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-已经是十四世纪了，现在…\N-现在我仍然是国王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:52.53,0:45:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我命令你赶快清醒过来，去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.06,0:45:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去娶我所爱的姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:56.63,0:46:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-再见父王\N-再见父王，去娶我所爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:00.20,0:46:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不，菲利，站住…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.11,0:46:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:10.05,0:46:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:33.50,0:46:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怎么对史帝芬交代呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.99,0:47:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧，快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:36.50,0:47:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，到这儿来，亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:44.44,0:47:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把门关好，蓝天\N翡翠，把帘子拉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:49.31,0:47:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，亲爱的，现在坐到这儿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.08,0:47:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我们给你的最后一个礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.59,0:48:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这象征庄严的皇冠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:01.86,0:48:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戴上它使你更加雍容美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.56,0:48:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它提醒你不要忘记\N皇家的权利和责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.27,0:48:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，亲爱的，来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:18.81,0:48:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧，让她一个人待一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.28,0:48:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因为那个男孩子\N咱们该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.16,0:49:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，我不明白\N为什么要她嫁一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:11.09,0:49:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老王子呢？\N不，这事由不得咱们，亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:27.21,0:49:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许该把那个男孩子的事\N告诉史帝芬国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:30.71,0:49:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-对啊，当然应该了\N-你们听…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:33.38,0:49:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是黑巫婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:34.92,0:49:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰\N-蔷薇玫瑰，蔷薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:38.25,0:49:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱们干嘛丢下她一个人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:40.46,0:49:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰？\N-蔷薇玫瑰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:02.78,0:50:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:04.61,0:50:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔷薇玫瑰，蔷薇玫瑰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.18,0:50:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-你在哪儿？\N-你在哪儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.19,0:50:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰，你在哪儿？\N-蔷薇玫瑰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.61,0:50:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰\N-蔷薇玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:35.48,0:50:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔷薇玫瑰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:45.45,0:50:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰\N-蔷薇玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:58.10,0:51:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰不要碰任何东西\N-不要，不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:03.34,0:51:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摸一下纺车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:06.01,0:51:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说摸一下纺车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.82,0:51:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们这些可怜的傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.72,0:51:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自以为能够战胜我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.16,0:51:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道吗？我是万恶女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:23.06,0:51:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是你们的宝贝公主!\N哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:33.80,0:51:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-蔷薇玫瑰，我的蔷薇玫瑰…\N-蔷薇玫瑰，我的蔷薇玫瑰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.21,0:51:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，天啊，我永远不能原谅自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:43.48,0:51:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们都有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:52.92,0:51:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有件事，史蒂芬…\N很重要的事，我得告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:57.79,0:51:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后再说吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:59.73,0:52:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是这是关于菲利的事\N-菲利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:03.03,0:52:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，对了，当然\N菲利他跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.80,0:52:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这正是我要告诉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:09.07,0:52:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上派人把他找来呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:10.67,0:52:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是…\N-嘘!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:14.84,0:52:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太阳已经下山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:17.21,0:52:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备欢迎公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:21.48,0:53:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国王和王后真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.18,0:53:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果他们知道，心都要碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:28.92,0:53:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看不要让他们知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.92,0:53:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-可是…\N-咱们让所有的人都睡过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:36.63,0:53:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到蔷薇玫瑰醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.60,0:53:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.54,0:54:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可爱睡美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:02.99,0:54:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黄金秀发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:06.76,0:54:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阳光染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:12.70,0:54:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朱唇艳过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:16.03,0:54:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:20.34,0:54:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,梦里爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:24.87,0:54:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:29.88,0:54:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:30.91,0:54:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.92,0:54:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.05,0:54:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,披朝霞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:40.89,0:54:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从天降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:46.90,0:54:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的初吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.47,0:54:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将使你苏醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:55.34,0:54:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:57.51,0:55:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡美人安睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:05.58,0:55:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那爱情的初吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:09.45,0:55:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使你苏醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:14.92,0:55:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:17.76,0:55:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:22.77,0:55:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:33.48,0:55:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听我说菲利这孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.55,0:55:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像爱上了一个什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:42.99,0:55:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,农家姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:44.39,0:55:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,农家姑娘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:46.99,0:55:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有呢？接着说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:50.69,0:55:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,农家姑娘是谁？\N他在哪里遇见她的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:54.26,0:55:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遇见了一个农家姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:57.27,0:55:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在什么地方？在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.23,0:56:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在他的梦里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.67,0:56:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在梦里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:05.24,0:56:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔷薇玫瑰，菲利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:13.45,0:56:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快来，咱们得赶快回到小木屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.33,0:57:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:35.50,0:57:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，这可真是一个令人高兴的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:40.70,0:57:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我张开网要捉一个农民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:43.64,0:57:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到抓到了一个王子，哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.98,0:57:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把他带走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:52.65,0:57:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心一点，我的宝贝，小心一点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:57.12,0:58:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位皇家客人能帮我实现计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.56,0:58:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，是黑巫婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:35.92,0:58:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她抓走了菲利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.69,0:58:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,带到她的魔窟去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:41.76,0:58:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，我们不能去那里啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:45.23,0:58:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们能去，我们必须去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.21,1:01:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可惜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:10.65,1:01:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利王子不能到这儿来\N和我们一起庆祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:17.19,1:01:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走，咱们到地牢里去安慰安慰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:15.18,1:02:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，菲利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:17.98,1:02:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么这么不高兴呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.65,1:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有着美好的前程
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:24.12,1:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你将使神话中的英雄故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:28.19,1:02:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变成真实
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:35.03,1:02:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看在史帝芬国王的城堡里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.34,1:02:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那个最高的塔楼上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.74,1:02:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奥萝拉公主正在作着美梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.51,1:02:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她以一个农家姑娘的面貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:53.88,1:02:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赢得了一个王子的爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.22,1:03:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她真是一个可爱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.63,1:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阳光般的金发
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.23,1:03:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玫瑰花般的红唇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:10.83,1:03:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在漫长的睡眠中守着一个信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:15.90,1:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等待着心上人的一个吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:21.91,1:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岁月如梭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:24.58,1:03:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利王子一往情深，痴心不改
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:30.65,1:03:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一百年后的一天，地牢的门打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.29,1:03:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重获自由的王子骑着他高贵的战马
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.36,1:03:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他勇猛威武地奔向他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.77,1:03:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心爱的姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:46.94,1:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用他的爱和初吻将她唤醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:52.67,1:03:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以证明真挚的爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.24,1:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以战胜一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:00.98,1:04:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-哈…哈…哈…\N-你这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:06.76,1:04:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧，宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:08.66,1:04:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让尊贵的王子\N和他的梦想待在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:18.23,1:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，真是令人兴奋的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:25.87,1:04:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十六年来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.34,1:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我第一次可以好好的睡上一觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:48.00,1:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘘，没有时间解释了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.47,1:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.58,1:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利王子，在爱情的道路上\N还有艰难险阻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.98,1:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要有勇气面对它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.42,1:05:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,带上给你的这块\N威力无边的美德之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:12.99,1:05:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和这支强大无比的正义之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:16.56,1:05:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们可以帮助你战胜邪恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:20.80,1:05:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧，必须赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.41,1:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲利，小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:08.57,1:07:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安静，你去告诉那些笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:12.64,1:07:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢，噢，不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.12,1:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心点，菲利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.06,1:07:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快，赶快，菲利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:44.84,1:07:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让荆棘组成他的坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.58,1:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天上降下死亡之雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.51,1:07:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的咒语如电闪雷鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:56.12,1:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他无法接近史帝芬的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:50.17,1:08:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，这不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.95,1:09:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在你得和我较量，王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:03.45,1:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是无敌的万恶女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:51.13,1:09:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上来，从这儿上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:09.72,1:10:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用真理之剑，快速出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:12.75,1:10:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邪恶必死无疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.43,1:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起，哈伯，我喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.16,1:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才你你说什么来着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.27,1:12:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我，我说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:08.60,1:12:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔，对了，不管怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:11.87,1:12:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在已经是十四世纪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:15.54,1:12:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对，十四世纪，你刚刚说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.78,1:12:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是直截了当地告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:21.92,1:12:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的儿子菲利说他要娶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.32,1:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的儿子菲利说他要娶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:50.48,1:12:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是奥萝拉，她来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:57.72,1:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和菲利在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:14.54,1:13:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这，这是怎么一回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:17.07,1:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我，我不明白…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.78,1:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,儿子，我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.52,1:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.71,1:14:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔，翡翠，你怎么了？亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:01.68,1:14:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，我喜欢大团圆的结局
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:05.75,1:14:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，我也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.86,1:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.30,1:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,粉红
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:16.46,1:14:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.20,1:14:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾与你在我梦中游
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:21.54,1:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.57,1:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:27.11,1:14:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那熟悉的眼神看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:32.68,1:14:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:35.22,1:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现实不都像梦境般美好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:40.69,1:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信你我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:42.52,1:14:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将一见钟情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:45.26,1:14:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就如梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:47.36,1:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情景一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:49.60,1:14:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无限
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:54.60,1:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美好


